{"tid":2007757,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"柒婆的自信 - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-05-08T13:32:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T16:38:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b4254fb410e15027fad3924468de778488b936aa","tid":2007757,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T13:32:17.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200508/20914024/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200508%2F20914024%2F&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQFScv4UPbHgCWRxxYzHlmUY%3D&h=11ce7f1d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200508%2F20914024%2F&h=6bed5bb2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200508/20914024/</a><br />\n<br />\n柒婆的自信 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200508/large/1588832707_c3fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200508%2Flarge%2F1588832707_c3fd.jpg&h=4a35d848&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府派罩，由柒婆做模特戴上「銅芯」口罩，親身示範，有驚人反效果。<br />\n<br />\n這款淺色底配上幼條紋的布口罩，看起來闊大鬆垮，被網民嘲諷為阿婆底褲。有人找到中資百貨公司棉質底褲的相片放上網絡，乍眼看，質地與「銅芯」口罩相似。柒婆戴上它，本來不算小的臉孔上只剩下一對陰冷的三角小眼及小眼下的大眼袋，真的有點像一個找不到口罩的阿婆急於使用口罩，隨手從櫃桶拿出一條鬆鬆垮垮的底褲包到臉上。<br />\n<br />\n一個為了禁止香港人戴口罩不惜上法庭打官司，並。。。。。。。。。。。無其事戴口罩現身人前，已經很匪夷所思。戴得那麼難看，還敢親身示。。。。。。。。。。。。像的。<br />\n<br />\n要推銷一件不討好的商品，必須找到對的人。比如。。。。。。。。。。。。偶像說吃蝙蝠可以抵抗武漢肺炎，粉絲都說「對對對」，找到這樣一個。。。。。。。。。。。。。女，可以化腐朽為神奇，再老土的阿婆底褲戴到他們臉上，或者着到。。。。。。。。。。。。。以為老土產品能反襯出他們身上的時尚氣質。找對人了，就容易辦了。<br />\n<br />\n不知柒婆哪來的自信，形象一敗塗地，竟敢示範。。。。。。。。。。。。。。款口罩非常「同心」。 <br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk"},{"pid":"01e80c7ea77c5ef27fe939495346dda8ce4b7cfe","tid":2007757,"uid":73619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T13:35:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e5ea616e4d4809f6970cd0ccfa61d4727ef2b7","tid":2007757,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T13:53:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />."},{"pid":"9830661d60918766f027046e6e173f93801672fc","tid":2007757,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T16:34:00.000Z","msg":"佢當年係讀特殊學校，所以年年考第一?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a163042208af70baa8cc7f552e3deb7448fbdf","tid":2007757,"uid":275302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T16:38:19.000Z","msg":"但有二百萬人登記咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}